    <!---->
    <!---->
    <para><para xml:id="idg-all-esx-vcenter_credential_update-xml-4"><phrase><phrase/></phrase></para></para>

    <para>This procedure updates the IP address, user name, password and/or port of the vCenter in the
      EON service if any of those values are changed. </para>

    <orderedlist xml:id="idg-all-esx-vcenter_credential_update-xml-6">
        <listitem><para>Execute the following
            command:</para>
<screen >eon resource-manager-update [--ip-address &lt;RESOURCE_MANGER_IP_ADDR&gt;] [--username &lt;RESOURCE_MANGER_USERNAME&gt;] [--password &lt;RESOURCE_MANGER_PASSWORD&gt;] [--port &lt;RESOURCE_MANGER_PORT&gt;] &lt;RESOURCE_MANGER_ID&gt;</screen><para>Where: </para>
<itemizedlist>
              <listitem><para>Resource Manager IP address - the IP address of the vCenter server.</para>
</listitem>
              <listitem><para>Resource Manager Username - the admin privilege username for the vCenter.</para>
</listitem>
              <listitem><para>Resource Manager Password - the password for the above username.</para>
</listitem>
              <listitem><para>Resource Manager Port - the vCenter server port. By default it is 443.</para>
</listitem>
              <listitem><para>Resource Manager ID - the ID for the vCenter server </para>
</listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
<para><emphasis role="bold">Sample
            Output</emphasis></para>
<screen >eon resource-manager-update --username root --password gone2far 2A6FC852-5F5E-4206-B6CC-C85E6B62A367
+-------------+--------------------------------------+
| Property    | Value                                |
+-------------+--------------------------------------+
| ID          | 2A6FC852-5F5E-4206-B6CC-C85E6B62A367 |
| IPv4Address | 10.1.200.17                          |
| Name        | 10.1.200.17                          |
| Password    | &lt;SANITIZED&gt;                          |
| Port        | 443                                  |
| State       | registered                           |
| Type        | vcenter                              |
| Username    | root                                 |
+-------------+--------------------------------------+</screen>
</listitem>
      </orderedlist>

  </section>
